        },
        {
            "title": "彰銀Q1賺52.21億元創新高 EPS 0.44元 獲利3本柱皆雙位數成長",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pi0LLUgl9e.je4cMye5vjQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/3c8540058515e1d112b6f02e06caa6d5\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
